data.description: THIS IS SUCH A GREAT HOME AT A GREAT PRICE!!!! Ready for you! Awesome home in Rigby Idaho. Just down the block from Harwood Elementary School. The kitchen has been updated with butcher block countertops, refaced cabinets and new appliances. The main floor is hardwood flooring throughout. So much storage space. Newer windows and metal roof and siding. The basement is partially unfinished and ready to make your own. Sellers are finishing up some trim work in the kitchen.
